  "title": "Flavorful Middle Eastern Potatoes Tagine",
  "description": "A lazy Sunday Middle Eastern dish featuring floury potatoes, pickle, and cheese pull, cooked in a fondue pot. This umami rich dish is perfect for a relaxing day.",
