  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the fondue pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the cubed potatoes, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Cook the potatoes for 15 minutes, or until they are tender and lightly browned.",
    "Stir in the chopped pickle and crumbly feta cheese.",
    "Continue to cook for an additional 5 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and the potatoes are fully coated.",
    "Serve the potatoes hot, garnished with additional pickle and feta cheese if desired.",
    "Use crusty bread or pita chips to scoop up the flavorful potatoes and cheese."
